Task: Implement an EarlyStopping callback that stops training 
if validation loss doesn’t improve for 
3 epochs and restores the best weights.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

import tensorflow as t

def f():
    cb = t.keras.callbacks.EarlyStopping(
        monitor="val_loss",
        patience=3,
        restore_best_weights=True
    )
    return cb

